         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The collection of documents was acquired by gift and purchase from various sources between 1941 and 1973. Source information is recorded at the folder level in the contents list. For further information, consult the appropriate curator.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
